If you want to see your app running on root you need to set `output.publicPath` to root.
Try this:
```js
output: {
    path: path.resolve(__dirname, &#39;/dist&#39;),
    filename: &#39;bundle.js&#39;,
    publicPath: &#39;/&#39;
},
```

Also you need to set `devServer.contentBase` to your build directory:
```js
devServer: {
    contentBase: path.resolve(__dirname, &#39;/dist&#39;),
    // ...
}
```

